<a class="title title-3 js-editableItem" href="/ct/2024/april/strange-religion-nijay-gupta-first-christians-roman-empire.html">Confronting the 21st-Century Church with the First-Century Church</a><div class="deck  spacer-top-5" data-id="202770">Nijay Gupta helps us rediscover the compelling strangeness of the earliest Christians.</div>
<div class="byline spacer-top-8"><span class="author">Ed Creedy</span><span class="pipe">|</span><span class="postdate "><time datetime="2024-3-18">March 18, 2024 </time></span></div>
</li><li class="card spacer-bottom-25 js-editableItem" data-type="article" data-id="202772"><div class="slug "><a class="js-clickTrack" data-category="" data-action="Breadcrumbs Section" data-label="excerpt" href="/ct/search?type=contenttype&contenttype=excerpt&order=newest">Excerpt</a></div>
<a class="title title-3 js-editableItem" href="/ct/2024/april/defiant-joy-jennifer-michelle-greenberg.html">O Ye of Overconfident Faith</a><div class="deck  spacer-top-5" data-id="202772">Like the disciples, we need to learn the difference between trust in Jesus and spiritual cockiness.</div>
<div class="byline spacer-top-8"><span class="author">Jennifer Michelle Greenberg</span><span class="pipe">|</span><span class="postdate "><time datetime="2024-3-18">March 18, 2024 </time></span></div>
